# c x a is fully materialized. Only the final join with b receives the ordered top-N discount.
query ITTII nosort
EXPLAIN SELECT a.id, b.id, c.id
FROM p8_oa a JOIN p8_ob b ON a.id > 0 CROSS JOIN p8_oc c
ORDER BY c.id LIMIT 2
